sub_title: Studying the sustainable energy revolution at Hanze University of Applied Science
summary: My goal is to use my education and experience to create a more sustainable future. I believe that sustainability and the circular economy is not only good for the environment but also for people and business. I am excited to contribute to this important field and drive change for a better future. Able to handle large projects to balance deadlines with multiple stakeholders.
